01:08:30,440 --> 01:08:32,108
We made it.

515
01:08:40,325 --> 01:08:42,160
[groaning]

516
01:08:47,999 --> 01:08:49,626
Surge.

517
01:08:49,667 --> 01:08:51,127
[groaning]

518
01:08:51,210 --> 01:08:52,795
You're going
to make it.

519
01:08:52,837 --> 01:08:54,631
You're going
to be all right.

520
01:08:54,714 --> 01:08:57,675
Hold on.
Please, please,
please, please, brother.

521
01:08:57,759 --> 01:08:59,594
Stay with me.

522
01:09:01,137 --> 01:09:02,680
Just hold on.
Please.

523
01:09:02,764 --> 01:09:04,807
[groaning]

524
01:09:07,143 --> 01:09:10,146
Surge.
Stay with me.

525
01:09:10,188 --> 01:09:12,899
Hey.
Stay with me.

526
01:09:12,982 --> 01:09:15,026
Stay with me.

527
01:09:15,109 --> 01:09:17,403
Please.
Please, brother.

528
01:09:17,487 --> 01:09:20,657
Stay with me.
I need your help.

529
01:09:48,976 --> 01:09:50,812
[groaning]

530
01:10:04,033 --> 01:10:07,036
L...need you, brother.

531
01:10:18,005 --> 01:10:20,633
I can't do this alone.

532
01:10:23,636 --> 01:10:25,638
Father chose

533
01:10:27,056 --> 01:10:29,058
the right son.

534
01:10:39,819 --> 01:10:41,237
[grunts]

535
01:11:00,465 --> 01:11:02,633
This will slow down
the poison.

536
01:11:04,761 --> 01:11:06,637
Now rest.

537
01:11:08,931 --> 01:11:10,433
Rest.

538
01:11:12,435 --> 01:11:13,853
Impressive.

539
01:11:13,936 --> 01:11:15,438
You put up
quite a fight.

540
01:11:15,480 --> 01:11:16,689
I didn't think
you had it in you.

541
01:11:19,525 --> 01:11:21,319
The assassination,
I know you didn't do it.

542
01:11:21,402 --> 01:11:24,697
What a revelation.

543
01:11:24,781 --> 01:11:27,700
Are you finally
admitting your guilt?

544
01:11:58,940 --> 01:12:01,734
Three witnesses
saw you.

545
01:12:01,818 --> 01:12:04,320
They saw
an illusion.

546
01:12:22,672 --> 01:12:24,090
Do it, you coward.

547
01:12:27,760 --> 01:12:29,095
Kill me.

548
01:12:29,178 --> 01:12:30,888
Who is headed
to my village?

549
01:12:30,972 --> 01:12:32,723
What village?

550
01:12:32,807 --> 01:12:34,559
Who killed Fumitaka?

551
01:12:34,642 --> 01:12:35,977
You did.

552
01:12:38,980 --> 01:12:40,314
Didn't you?

553
01:13:48,424 --> 01:13:50,092
Brother.

554
01:13:51,177 --> 01:13:52,595
Hey.

555
01:13:52,637 --> 01:13:54,764
Where are we?

556
01:13:54,847 --> 01:13:57,099
Home, Surge.
Home.

557
01:13:58,768 --> 01:14:00,436
The poison
is moving again.

558
01:14:00,478 --> 01:14:02,688
We need to get you back
to the village now.

559
01:14:02,772 --> 01:14:04,774
Water.

560
01:14:04,857 --> 01:14:07,777
Okay, I'll be back
in a second.

561
01:14:16,160 --> 01:14:18,412
<i>[water running]</i>

562
01:14:45,940 --> 01:14:47,024
Brother?

563
01:14:47,108 --> 01:14:49,151
Ahh.
No!

564
01:14:57,743 --> 01:15:00,079
Reveal yourself.

565
01:15:02,289 --> 01:15:04,834
Every clan has
their secret weapon.

566
01:15:06,752 --> 01:15:09,380
But I have the most
powerful one of them all.

567
01:15:12,591 --> 01:15:14,427
Deceit.

568
01:15:22,518 --> 01:15:25,855
<i>[muted chanting]</i>

569
01:15:52,256 --> 01:15:54,550
<i>You killed
our master.</i>

570
01:15:54,633 --> 01:15:57,762
Why?
When did you become
so naive?

571
01:16:02,475 --> 01:16:05,144
You have no honor.
No respect for the Code.

572
01:16:05,227 --> 01:16:07,688
I live
by my own code.

573
01:16:16,072 --> 01:16:19,992
You had everything.
No, I had nothing.

574
01:16:21,660 --> 01:16:25,915
Master Fumitaka
always loved you most.

575
01:16:25,956 --> 01:16:29,919
I knew you would
always be my enemy.

576
01:16:30,002 --> 01:16:31,837
Fumitaka chose you.

577
01:16:31,921 --> 01:16:34,882
Only because
I made it so.

578
01:17:01,909 --> 01:17:04,787
<i>When we were young,</i>

579
01:17:04,870 --> 01:17:07,456
my deceit was subtle.

580
01:17:07,540 --> 01:17:11,669
Master Fumitaka
seeing you steal
an apple

581
01:17:11,752 --> 01:17:15,965
or hearing you tell
a little white lie.

582
01:17:16,006 --> 01:17:20,136
Before long,
he couldn't quite
trust you.

583
01:17:20,177 --> 01:17:22,304
That made him very sad.

584
01:17:22,388 --> 01:17:26,642
<i>It broke his poor
little heart.</i>

585
01:17:26,684 --> 01:17:30,646
Needless to say,
I started looking
very promising to him.

586
01:17:30,729 --> 01:17:33,149
He gave you everything.
No.

587
01:17:33,232 --> 01:17:36,652
I waited years
to take over the clan.

588
01:17:36,735 --> 01:17:39,738
But our beloved Fumitaka

589
01:17:39,822 --> 01:17:41,991
decided to call
for peace,

590
01:17:42,032 --> 01:17:46,162
<i>bring you and all
the others back
into the fold.</i>

591
01:17:48,622 --> 01:17:50,499
<i>[thundering]</i>

592
01:18:08,017 --> 01:18:09,268
<i>[shouting]</i>

593
01:18:46,805 --> 01:18:48,766
Ahh!

594
01:18:52,811 --> 01:18:55,272
I intercepted
his message.

595
01:18:55,356 --> 01:18:57,816
He was going
to make you
his second.

596
01:19:00,486 --> 01:19:03,447
<i>Seeing you as master
of the Lost Clan,</i>

597
01:19:03,530 --> 01:19:07,243
<i>upholding the Code
so well.</i>

598
01:19:07,284 --> 01:19:10,412
Practically
made me vomit.

599
01:19:10,454 --> 01:19:13,457
That is why now
you must die.

600
01:19:13,540 --> 01:19:15,584
<i>[grunting]</i>

601
01:19:15,668 --> 01:19:17,253
[yelling]

602
01:19:31,600 --> 01:19:33,394
Brother.
[groans]

603
01:19:43,028 --> 01:19:45,823
Cage of the Lost Clan,

604
01:19:47,533 --> 01:19:49,285
you are a great warrior

605
01:19:51,120 --> 01:19:53,122
and an honorable ninja.

606
01:19:58,585 --> 01:20:01,005
Asleader
of the Southern Clan,

607
01:20:02,798 --> 01:20:05,634
I promise you
your homeland
will be protected.

608
01:20:10,347 --> 01:20:13,392
Don't protect us.

609
01:20:13,475 --> 01:20:15,894
Respect us.

610
01:20:18,188 --> 01:20:21,442
Come on, brother.
Let's go home.

